OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fslowly push east this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, gradually weakening. Clear
OL,8,Fspells at first in the east with a few
OL,9,Ffog patches possible. Clearer skies
OL,10,Fdevelop in the north later towards
OL,11,Fdawn, turning colder here with frost
OL,12,Fpatches likely.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FRather cloudy across England
OL,15,Fand Wales with patchy outbreaks of
OL,16,Fdrizzle possible, but some brighter
OL,17,Fspells likely too. Dry and largely
OL,18,Fsunny across Scotland and Northern
OL,19,FIreland with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
